title: A set of equipment for the production of polyethylene bags (3-7 layers) US-F3B-TR-1300
title_uz: Polietilen paket ishlab chiqarish uskunalar jamlanmasi (3-7 qavat) US-F3B-TR-1300

title_en: A set of equipment for the production of polyethylene bags (3-7 layers) US-F3B-TR-1300
short_description: This US-F3B-TR-1300 model set of equipment serves for the production of polyethylene bags. The equipment has a production capacity of up to 160 kg of bags per hour, a total power of 120 kW, a screw speed of 10-100 rpm, and a total weight of 12 tons. The description below shows other models of this equipment and their prices differ.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-F3B-TR-1300 modeldagi uskunalar jamlanmasi polietilen paketlar ishlab chiqarish uchun xizmat qiladi. Uskuna soatiga 160 kg gacha paket ishlab chiqarish quvvatiga ega, umumiy quvvati 120 kW , vint tezligi 10-100 rpm va umumiy vazni esa 12 tonnani tashkil qiladi. Quyidagi tavsifda shu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ularning narxlari farqlandi.
